vera-plugin-power (0.24-1) devel; urgency=medium

  * power: send a notification when the main battery is reaching the EMPTY_THRESHOLD.
  * common: raise the EMPTY_THRESHOLD from 2 to 5.
  * common: add SAFE_HIBERNATE_THRESHOLD.
  * power: force the hibernation when the battery level reaches the SAFE_HIBERNATE_THRESHOLD.
  * power: send notifications on battery state changes
  * debian/control: build-depend on libnotify-dev.

